  "synopsis": "In a world of magic, Russel Raymond, a cursed third-rate mage from a fallen lineage, seeks a new fate. Banished from the academy, he scrapes by as a mercenary until his mother’s memento sparks a chance to return to the past. Rewinding to his academy days, Russel receives a new power, igniting his journey to reclaim his honor and rewrite his destiny. With this second chance he’s been given, will he finally soar like the dragon he was meant to be? \n\n(Source: Tapas)",
